---
globs: ["**/*.py", "**/magbyte-micro/**", "**/scripts/**"]
---

# MagByte Python rules

- All Python lives in magbyte-micro (FastAPI microservice) or /scripts/
- Never add .py files inside the Next.js /app directory
- Use type hints on all function signatures
- Mock data scripts go in /scripts/mock/ and must be named mock_*.py
- n8n workflow JSON lives in /scripts/n8n/ — do not modify without confirmation
- FastAPI endpoints must have docstrings describing input/output shape
